flowchart TD
    ALERT[New Alert] --> PROC[process_new_alert]
    EVENT[Security Event] --> LINK[link_event_to_offense]

    PROC --> FIND
    LINK --> FIND

    FIND{Open offense on host within 30min?}
    FIND -->|Yes| UPDATE[Update offense]
    FIND -->|No| CREATE[Create offense #N]

    UPDATE --> ADD[Add OffenseEvent link]
    CREATE --> ADD

    ADD --> META[Update metadata]
    META --> TL[Append timeline entry]
    META --> USR[Track related_users]
    META --> HOST[Track related_hosts]
    META --> RISK[Recalculate risk_level]
